. The fundamental charge-transfer absorption\nband edge has a complex structure and is positioned around $\\sim$2.8-3.0 eV.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 9 Oct 2017 18:21:39 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 7 Nov 2017 10:46:04 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 27 Nov 2017 16:13:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-12-06"}
